There's only one success to be able to spend your life in your own way. Christopher Morley

I remember back in 2008 when I was a US Army recruiter and thinking about my exit plan from the US Army. I was listening to an audiobook by Timothy Ferriss the 4-Hour Work Week. It was right there that moment that I decided that I wanted to live a different way without having a boss. It was a scary moment for me and also the best moment for me. Here it is today 2017 thank the Lord I am still working from home. You can truly have your dreams come true if you believe them and have the faith. Using affirmations in having a positive mental attitude are just some of the drivers that will allow you to have the lifestyle you want to live. Read books study people who are successful and you shall have what you seek.  If you like this post please comment or like share with a friend who needs this today.
